      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Draft Trade Repositories (Amendment and Transitional Provision) (EU exit) Regulations 2018
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Draft statutory instrument, which will make amendments to retained EU law related to the registration and supervision of trade repositories, to be laid under the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018. </p>

  </div>
</div>

